Class OrbitTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • OrbitTest

  • public class OrbitTest
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the test method that contains the main method and creates a new JFrame. In the main method, an object of type Orbit is created. Additionally, an object of type executor service is created and executed so that the code in Orbit contains a run method which creates a new thread to allow the planet to move around the GUI.
